Package: readSRMtxt
Type: Package
Title: Convert a SRM txt file into a matrix. 
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-04-23
Author: David Garcia
Maintainer: David Garcia <dgseis@hotmail.es>
Description: Convert a SRM text file into a class object. This class object include: sample name, chromatographic retention time range, number of transitions and chromatographic time-intensity matrix (TI_matrix). TI_matrix contain: a time variable in the first column, intensity signal variables in the following columns for each transition.
License: GPL (>=2)
Depends: stringr, R (>= 2.14)
